title: SpectraLLM
abstract: >-
  Self-hosted, domain-specialized LLM builder: document ingestion,
  multi-strategy RAG (hybrid search, re-ranking, agentic/corrective/adaptive),
  and integrated QLoRA + DPO fine-tuning — fully local, no cloud dependency.
